com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto

Interface ITeamAreaPrivateScope

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IReadScope

    public interface ITeamAreaPrivateScope
extends IReadScope
    Items with this scope must be owned by a team area. Only members of the team area (and its descendant team areas) may view the item.
    Since:
    0.8.1.
